side-effects:
Side-effects nausea, vomiting, dyspepsia, abdominal pain, diarrhoea,
stomatitis, dry mouth, anorexia; dyspnoea; dizziness, syncope, asthenia,
paraesthesia, tremor, fatigue, drowsiness; pyrexia; vaginal haemorrhage;
myalgia; blood disorders (including anaemia, leucopenia, neutropenia,
thrombocytopenia, and increased myelosuppression); alopecia, pruritus;
peripheral oedema, injection-site reactions including phlebitis; also reported  secondary malignancies
